en_336770_0	Hindu priests (Kurukkal) at Alankulam Pullayar Kovil in Thunukkai, Kilinochchi honoured the Army by inviting Major General Kumar Peiris, General Officer Commanding, 65 Division to be one of the distinguished guests for the cornerstone-laying ceremony for a new building at the temple premises on Thursday (5).
en_336770_1	The head priest has personally extended the invitation as a gesture of goodwill that prevails between the Army and civilians in the area.
en_336770_2	At the auspicious minute, the GOC also joined the occasion by laying a cornerstone.
